headline: The year in review: Garmin releases 2024 Garmin Connect Data Report
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today released its 2024 Garmin Connect™ Data Report, highlighting overall health and fitness trends from its customers around the world. From detailed health and wellness stats – like how well our customers slept or how their bodies responded to stress – to fitness-driven data like average daily steps, insights from the Garmin Connect community show 2024 was another very active year.
